Reviews: The numbers are Klingon, but amazing if your a star wars fan
Very pleased to have purchased this one.
Easy to move around the house with the magnetic back
A very simple temp gauge. Looks and works as expected. Ideally the screen would be bigger to enable it to be read from more of a distance but I couldn't find anything like that

Works perfectly. The temperature matches our baby monitor so I can tell it is accurate. This has been a sturdy little room thermometer. It is sensitive to changing temperatures and updates quickly. It has given me so much piece of mind when working out what to dress my baby in at night.
Received promptly. I have it outside under the patio attached to metal shelves. Working well. Recommend.
Excellent little product. I'm unsure of the accuracy, but I tested it a little bit and it seems to be good.
Quality unit. Easy to use. Steal for its price
VERY GOOD EXCELLENT MAGNETIC ATTATCH

Amazing little device, had for couple of months now and still going strong and the original batteries. I got it as a happy medium between the baby monitor camera temperature sensor and the Sensibo sensor for controlling our AC. The camera is mounted high on the wall and was never be accurate because heat rises and the Sensibo sensor has to be near the AC so kt tells you it's freezing cold when in fact it's eight under the airflow. I have this gadget near our bub's red light and it has final say on temperature for dressing bub for nighttime.Also good to note, it does NOT have button batteries, just one AAA.
